adium","caption":"Suncorp Stadium","photographer":"","copyright":"","sequenceNumber":"100"},{"marketVariantId":"","multimediaId":"6a1649f5ce0b1d821cfc02c0","authoredDate":"2026-06-03","serverPath":"https://assets.atdw-online.com.au/images/b2834e8ba3ec3c230b76c44e311bc7d7.jpeg?rect=1%2C0%2C2364%2C1330&w=800&h=450&rot=360&q=eyJ0eXBlIjoibGlzdGluZyIsImxpc3RpbmdJZCI6IjZhMTYyZDE5ZWFmNjIxNjM0YWY4MjYwMiIsImRpc3RyaWJ1dG9ySWQiOiI1NmIxZWI5MzQ0ZmVjYTNkZjJlMzIwY2IiLCJhcGlrZXlJZCI6IjU2YjFlZmVlMGNmMjEzYWQyMGRkMjE3MCJ9","attributeIdMultimediaContent":"IMAGE","attributeIdMultimediaContentDescription":"Image","attributeIdSizeOrientation":"16X9","width":"800","height":"450","altText":"Suncorp Stadium","caption":"Suncorp Stadium","photographer":"","copyright":"","sequenceNumber":"100"},{"marketVariantId":"","multimediaId":"6a1649f5ce0b1d821cfc02c0","authoredDate":"2026-06-03","serverPath":"https://assets.atdw-online.com.au/images/b2834e8ba3ec3c230b76c44e311bc7d7.jpeg?rect=1%2C0%2C2364%2C1330&w=280&h=158&rot=360&q=eyJ0eXBlIjoibGlzdGluZyIsImxpc3RpbmdJZCI6IjZhMTYyZDE5ZWFmNjIxNjM0YWY4MjYwMiIsImRpc3RyaWJ1dG9ySWQiOiI1NmIxZWI5MzQ0ZmVjYTNkZjJlMzIwY2IiLCJhcGlrZXlJZCI6IjU2YjFlZmVlMGNmMjEzYWQyMGRkMjE3MCJ9","attributeIdMultimediaContent":"IMAGE","attributeIdMultimediaContentDescription":"Image","attributeIdSizeOrientation":"16X9","width":"280","height":"158","altText":"Suncorp Stadium","caption":"Suncorp Stadium","photographer":"","copyright":"","sequenceNumber":"100"}],"openTimes":[],"productComments":[{"marketVariantId":"English / Global","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ENGLISH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"English","commentText":"Don't miss this opportunity to step inside Brisbane's most iconic sporting venue like never before. This bus trip will take you on an exclusive guided tour of Suncorp Stadium where you will visit the dressing rooms, sidelines, media rooms, coaches box and more! Learn all about the rich sporting and cultural history of this historic site. Afterwards, enjoy a three-course meal at the Garden Room Cafe, situated amongst the beautiful Roma St Parklands."},{"marketVariantId":"Japanese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"JAPANESE","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Japanese","commentText":"ブリスベンで最も象徴的なスポーツ会場に、かつてないほど深く足を踏み入れるこの機会をお見逃しなく。このバスツアーでは、サンコープ・スタジアムの特別なガイド付きツアーにご案内し、ロッカールーム、サイドライン、メディア室、コーチボックスなどを見学します。この歴史的な場所の豊かなスポーツと文化の歴史について学びましょう。ツアー後は、美しいローマ・ストリート・パークランドに囲まれたガーデンルーム・カフェで、3コースのお食事をお楽しみください。"},{"marketVariantId":"Korean","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"KOREAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Korean","commentText":"브리즈번에서 가장 상징적인 스포츠 경기장인 선콥 스타디움을 전에 없던 방식으로 둘러볼 수 있는 이 특별한 기회를 놓치지 마세요. 버스 투어를 통해 선콥 스타디움의 선수 대기실 경기장 옆 공간 미디어룸 감독석 등을 방문하며 경기장 곳곳을 탐험할 수 있습니다. 이 역사적인 장소의 풍부한 스포츠 및 문화 역사에 대해 알아보세요. 투어 후에는 아름다운 로마 스트리트 공원에 위치한 가든 룸 카페에서 3코스 만찬을 즐기실 수 있습니다."},{"marketVariantId":"French","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"FRENCH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"French","commentText":"Ne manquez pas cette occasion unique de découvrir le stade Suncorp, l'un des lieux sportifs les plus emblématiques de Brisbane, comme jamais auparavant. Cette excursion en bus vous propose une visite guidée exclusive du stade, avec au programme les vestiaires, les abords du terrain, les salles de presse, la loge des entraîneurs et bien plus encore ! Plongez dans la riche histoire sportive et culturelle de ce site historique. Ensuite, savourez un repas trois services au Garden Room Cafe, situé au cœur du magnifique parc Roma Street."},{"marketVariantId":"Italian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ITALIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Italian","commentText":"Non perdete l'occasione di entrare nel luogo più iconico di Brisbane come mai prima d'ora. Questo tour in autobus vi porterà in un esclusivo tour guidato del Suncorp Stadium, dove visiterete gli spogliatoi, le aree laterali, le sale stampa, la cabina degli allenatori e molto altro! Scoprirete tutto sulla ricca storia sportiva e culturale di questo luogo storico. In seguito, potrete gustare una cena di tre portate al Garden Room Cafe, immerso nello splendido Roma St Parklands."},{"marketVariantId":"Indonesian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"INDONESIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Indonesian","commentText":"Jangan lewatkan kesempatan ini untuk memasuki tempat olahraga paling ikonik di Brisbane seperti belum pernah sebelumnya. Perjalanan bus ini akan membawa Anda dalam tur eksklusif berpemandu ke Stadion Suncorp di mana Anda akan mengunjungi ruang ganti, pinggir lapangan, ruang media, kotak pelatih, dan banyak lagi! Pelajari semua tentang sejarah olahraga dan budaya yang kaya dari situs bersejarah ini. Setelah itu, nikmati makan malam tiga hidangan di Garden Room Cafe, yang terletak di tengah-tengah Taman Roma St yang indah."},{"marketVariantId":"German","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"GERMAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"German","commentText":"Verpassen Sie nicht diese einmalige Gelegenheit, Brisbanes legendärste Sportstätte hautnah zu erleben! Diese Busreise führt Sie exklusiv durch das Suncorp Stadium, wo Sie die Umkleidekabinen, die Seitenlinie, die Medienräume, die Trainerloge und vieles mehr besichtigen. Erfahren Sie alles über die reiche Sport- und Kulturgeschichte dieses historischen Ortes. Anschließend genießen Sie ein Drei-Gänge-Menü im Garden Room Cafe inmitten der wunderschönen Roma Street Parklandschaft."},{"marketVariantId":"Portuguese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"PORT-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Portuguese","commentText":"Não perca esta oportunidade de conhecer o interior do estádio esportivo mais icônico de Brisbane como nunca antes. Este passeio de ônibus levará você a uma visita guiada exclusiva pelo Suncorp Stadium, onde você visitará os vestiários, as laterais do campo, as salas de imprensa, a cabine dos treinadores e muito mais! Aprenda tudo sobre a rica história esportiva e cultural deste local histórico. Depois, desfrute de uma refeição de três pratos no Garden Room Cafe, situado no belo Roma St Parklands."},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Simplified","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-S","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Simplified","commentText":"千万别错过这次以前所未有的方式走进布里斯班最具标志性的体育场馆的机会！这次巴士之旅将带您进行桑科体育场 (Suncorp Stadium) 的专属导览游，您将参观更衣室、场边、媒体室、教练席等等！深入了解这座历史遗址丰富的体育和文化底蕴。之后，您将在位于美丽的罗马街公园 (Roma St Parklands) 内的花园咖啡厅 (Garden Room Cafe) 享用三道菜的美味佳肴。"},{"marketVariantId":"Spanish","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"SPAN-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Spanish","commentText":"No te pierdas esta oportunidad de adentrarte en el recinto deportivo más emblemático de Brisbane como nunca antes. Este viaje en autobús te llevará en una visita guiada exclusiva al Estadio Suncorp, donde visitarás los vestuarios, las zonas de banquillo, las salas de prensa, el palco de entrenadores y mucho más. Descubre la rica historia deportiva y cultural de este lugar histórico. Después, disfruta de una comida de tres platos en el Garden Room Cafe, ubicado en el hermoso parque de Roma Street."},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Traditional","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-T","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Traditional","commentText":"千萬別錯過這次以前所未有的方式走進布里斯班最具代表性的體育場館的機會！這次巴士之旅將帶您進行桑科體育場 (Suncorp Stadium) 的專屬導覽遊，您將參觀更衣室、場邊、媒體室、教練席等等！深入了解這座歷史遺址豐富的運動和文化底蘊。之後，您將在位於美麗的羅馬街公園 (Roma St Parklands) 內的花園咖啡廳 (Garden Room Cafe) 享用三道菜的美味佳餚。"}],"productSite":[{"siteName":"YMCA Springfield Lakes Community Centre","attributeIdSiteType":"VENUE","attributeIdSiteTypeDescription":"Venue","productSiteAddressRelationship":[{"attributeIdAddress":"PHYSICAL","attributeIdAddressDescription":"Physical","addressLine1":"53 Springfield Lakes Boulevard","addressLine2":"","suburbName":"","cityName":"Springfield Lakes","areaName":"","stateName":"Queensland","countryName":"Australia","addressPostalCode":"4300","overrideDomesticRegionFlag":"0","geocodeGdaLatitude":"-27.6686128","geocodeGdaLongitude":"152.9216121","productSiteAddressStreetDirectoryRelationship":""}],"productSiteAttributeRelationship":"","productSiteCommentRelationship":"","productSiteCommunicationRelationship":"","productSiteLicenceRelationship":"","productSiteRelatedSiteRelationship":"","productSiteMultimediaRelationship":"","productSiteContactRelationship":""}],"mediaLinks":[],"alternateNames":[{"name":"Y-Care South East Queensland","kind":""}],"internationalReach":"","rates":[{"ratesType":"ALLTICKETS","ratesTypeDescription":"All tickets","priceFrom":"65","priceTo":"65","free":"","rate